# ─── Purchased Unity Asset Store packs (license protection) ─────────
# These packs have Unity_AssetStore_standard license which FORBIDS
# redistribution of source files in public repos. Each pack imports
# into Assets/ under its own folder. Add each pack's folder name here
# as it gets imported. The Forever engine repo is public on GitHub so
# this is a license-critical defense.
#
# Note: the pack folders contain meshes, textures, materials, prefabs,
# and demo scenes that are essential for the game at runtime. They're
# gitignored because they can be re-imported from Unity Package Manager
# by anyone who has purchased them on their Unity account.
#
# Purchased 2026-04-09 ($452.72 total):
# Extracted from .unitypackage cache to Assets/ on 2026-04-09.
# Actual folder names (confirmed after extraction):
